{"tid":628282,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現原來做人真係可以咁開心","createTime":"2018-04-13T16:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T06:04:32.000Z","uid":126569,"like":13,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ced8a2f71f00bfb69e4670a5d671e1092fd4c387","tid":628282,"uid":126569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"話說我鐘意左個女仔<br />\n<br />\n咁個女仔身邊就有個男性朋友好親既，中學同學黎<br />\n<br />\n咁啱得咁橋，原來我地三個係互相都認識<br />\n<br />\n姐係我識條仔，又識條女，但係條女唔知原來我識條仔咁樣<br />\n<br />\n咁打打下機相認左之後就好多時三人行一齊出街<br />\n<br />\n咁我問過條仔，你地識左咁多年，真係無FEEL咩<br />\n<br />\n條仔誓神劈願話無野，大家知大家唔會鐘意對方<br />\n<br />\n咩就算條女除左衫訓係張床度都會直接叫佢死開<br />\n<br />\n我開頭都以為無乜野，條仔純粹係度相幫我地搭路乜乜乜咁樣<br />\n<br />\n直到近排我同個女仔嘈大交，佢先同我坦白話佢原來同條女係情人節搞過野<br />\n<br />\n重要係佢主動聊條女上床<br />\n<br />\n上完床重要係我面前扮無野<br />\n<br />\n條女出街食完飯叫我埋單完全無出過聲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大佬啊你唔撚係著撚左我對西瓜啊，你將成個西瓜笠撚左落我個頭啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係啊我同條女無一齊過，嚴格黎講唔算綠左我<br />\n<br />\n你東窗事發之後居然重話想同我繼續做兄弟<br />\n<br />\n你搞撚完連講都無同我講過，繼續要我做傻仔有時重要我請撚埋你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔係咁開心啊?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原來做人真係好開心啊我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6256452d41527f207e6de268153648e98588ce","tid":628282,"uid":138138,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"朋友妻 咪走雞<br />\n阿唔係，，，佢連你女友都唔係喎"},{"pid":"dbbda1cb6be55a6eb22205bbdfd06604ac70b66c","tid":628282,"uid":126569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1b6256452d41527f207e6de268153648e98588ce","tid":628282,"uid":138138,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"朋友妻 咪走雞<br />\n阿唔係，，，佢連你女友都唔係喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"啱啊<br />\n<br />\n所以佢又無綠我<br />\n<br />\n咁咪做得兄弟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058b0bf70cfd783a60eb46550b902ce3fa1ce7a2","tid":628282,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朋友妻 咪走雞<br />\n阿唔係，，，佢連你女友都唔係喎</blockquote>啱啊<br />\n<br />\n所以佢又無綠我<br />\n<br />\n咁咪做得兄弟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩係兄弟？<br />\n有着數個陣咪係"},{"pid":"da64d591b477669043b47a9ef2c7153785f0c74f","tid":628282,"uid":126569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"058b0bf70cfd783a60eb46550b902ce3fa1ce7a2","tid":628282,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朋友妻 咪走雞<br />\n阿唔係，，，佢連你女友都唔係喎</blockquote>啱啊<br />\n<br />\n所以佢又無綠我<br />\n<br />\n咁咪做得兄弟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩係兄弟？<br />\n有着數個陣咪係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"平時吃喝玩樂就差唔多要我請埋<br />\n<br />\n真係